<i>Je to roztomilé.

75
00:06:01,759 --> 00:06:02,560
<i>Nerozumíš tomu.

76
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:04,240
Co je to?

77
00:06:04,959 --> 00:06:05,839
Cože, kreslíš i kožešinu?

78
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,439
