271
00:13:59,039 --> 00:13:59,879
Jsi bohatý, co?

272
00:14:00,159 --> 00:14:00,799
Nemachruj,

273
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:01,960
víš, kdo jsem?

274
00:14:02,759 --> 00:14:03,919
<i>Nech to plavat,

275
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:04,920
