276
00:14:05,039 --> 00:14:06,240
<i>Víš, kdo já jsem?

277
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:09,320
Pojďme.

278
00:14:12,919 --> 00:14:13,679
Hele, kam jdeš?

279
00:14:13,679 --> 00:14:14,719
Zapomeň na to.

280
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:23,040
