337
00:17:24,829 --> 00:17:25,960
<i>Vidíte?

338
00:17:26,349 --> 00:17:28,549
Je to velmi snadný způsob?

339
00:17:28,759 --> 00:17:30,480
Dveřmi ořechy nikdo neotvírá,

340
00:17:30,680 --> 00:17:31,960
